      "text": "それでも私はダンスが好きで、続けていきたいから\n認めてもらうために頑張ってきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ I love dancing and want to keep doing it.\nThat’s why I’ve worked hard to prove myself to them.",
