      "text": "……いえ、認めてくれませんでした\nそれどころか……いつまで遊んでいるんだ、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn’t.\nIn fact… they berated me for wasting my time with such silly things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
