      "text": "さすがに我慢できなくって、口論になって……\n今はもう両親とは絶縁みたいな状態です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn’t take it anymore‚ and we ended up fighting over it…\nI’ve pretty much cut ties with them ever since.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
